Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放松
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺着我的节奏
